For example, when we were asking for contributions for literature,

00:15:31.429 --> 00:15:35.429
some brothers in Africa and other places couldn't afford to have a watchtower

00:15:35.429 --> 00:15:38.429
for every member of the family.

00:15:38.429 --> 00:15:41.429
They were just too poor.

00:15:41.429 --> 00:15:44.429
And what about bomb books?

00:15:44.429 --> 00:15:47.429
Tell you an experience in one African country.

