There was those taking the lead to saw a better way of doing things.

00:17:19.940 --> 00:17:22.940
They didn't hesitate to make adjustments.

00:17:22.940 --> 00:17:25.940
That's very faith strengthening.

00:17:25.940 --> 00:17:28.940
And the best is yet to come.

